          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "TOF",
                "ASSOP"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Measurement of the time of flight spectrum",
                " of neutrons scattered by a liquid nitrogen sample",
                " using a fast coincidence equipment detecting also the",
                " associated alpha particles of the H-3(d,n)He-4",
                " reaction.",
                ".Flight path 350 cm, time resolution of the spectro-",
                " meter 1.4 ns FWHM.",
                "Two measurements have been made, with the distributor",
                "of nitrogen and with his empty pot."
              ]
            }
          ],
